mil.nga.giat.geowave.accumulo.mapreduce.dedupe

Class GeoWaveDedupeJobRunner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.conf.Configured
      • mil.nga.giat.geowave.accumulo.mapreduce.dedupe.GeoWaveDedupeJobRunner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.hadoop.conf.Configurable, org.apache.hadoop.util.Tool

    public class GeoWaveDedupeJobRunner
extends org.apache.hadoop.conf.Configured
implements org.apache.hadoop.util.Tool
    This class can run a basic job to query GeoWave, deduplicating results, and writing the final set of key value pairs to a sequence file. It can be extended for more advanced capabilities or job chaining.
